messages.content: What does the comfyui-Image-reward integration collaborate with to convert the workflow into an app?
The comfyui-Image-reward integration collaborates with [mixlab-nodes](https://github.com/shadowcz007/comfyui-mixlab-nodes) to convert the workflow into an app.
What is the task of the ImageReward model?
The ImageReward model is for human preference learning in text-to-image generation.
Which professional large-scale dataset is the ImageReward model trained with?
The ImageReward model is trained with the ImageRewardDB dataset.
How many comparison pairs are there in the ImageRewardDB dataset?
There are approximately 137,000 comparison pairs in the ImageRewardDB dataset.
What is the name of the paper related to the ImageReward model?
The paper related to the ImageReward model is for NeurIPS 2023.
Where should the ImageReward and bert-base-uncased models be placed in ComfyUI?
The ImageReward.pt and med_config.json files should be placed in ComfyUI/models/image_reward/ and the bert-base-uncased model should be placed in ComfyUI/models/image_reward/bert-base-uncased/.
Does the comfyui-Image-reward integration provide a workflow example?
Yes, the comfyui-Image-reward integration provides a workflow example in ./example/image-reward-workflow.json.
